org.apache.lucene.queries.function.docvalues

Class LongDocValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.queries.function.FunctionValues
      • org.apache.lucene.queries.function.docvalues.LongDocValues

  • public abstract class LongDocValues
extends FunctionValues
    Abstract FunctionValues implementation which supports retrieving long values. Implementations can control how the long values are loaded through longVal(int)}
